---
title: Spiced Cauliflower & Pearl Couscous Salad with Roasted Pumpkin
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies like cauliflower and pumpkin with pearl couscous. Add Middle Eastern spices for extra flavour, then top it off with crumbly feta cheese.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
